 [Sanrio Vfes] Nijisanji VTuber Yuika Shiina、Himawari Honma 和 Ririmu Makai 将在 VRChat 上访问 Puroland！ https://www.moguravr.com/sanrio-vfes-nijisanji/ノンジャンル人生 Thu, 07 Mar 2024 09:11:46 +0000 VRChatVTuberにじさんじメタバースサンリオサンリオVfes https://www.moguravr.com/?p=247497 <p>在 VRChat 上直至 3 月 17 日星期日举行的虚拟活动“SANRIO Virtual Festival 2024 in Sanrio Puroland (Sanrio Vfes)”中，VTuber 团体“Nijisanji”[...]</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/sanrio-vfes-nijisanji/">[Sanrio Vfes] Nijisanji VTuber Yuika Shiina、Himawari Honma 和 Rimu Makai 将在 VRChat 上访问 Puroland！</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ; <p>据宣布，来自 VTuber 团体<strong>“</strong> <a href="https://www.nijisanji.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Nijisanji</strong></a> <strong>”</strong>的 VTuber 将参加虚拟活动<strong>“</strong> <a href="https://v-fes.sanrio.co.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>SANRIO Virtual Festival 2024 in Sanrio Puroland (Sanrio Vfes)</strong></a> <strong>”</strong> ，该活动在<a href="https://hello.vrchat.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">VRChat</a>上举行至 3 月 17 日星期日。计划访问时间为3月11日（星期一）。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f823fb3276f9355eb3945b749bb550b4-kix.1b73plpy4dz4-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f823fb3276f9355eb3945b749bb550b4-kix.1b73plpy4dz4-jpg.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f823fb3276f9355eb3945b749bb550b4-kix.1b73plpy4dz4-jpg.webp 1000w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f823fb3276f9355eb3945b749bb550b4-kix.1b73plpy4dz4-300x225.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f823fb3276f9355eb3945b749bb550b4-kix.1b73plpy4dz4-768x576.webp 768w" width="1000" height="750" /></a></p><p>在 Sanrio Vfes，我们一直在实施一个项目，让受欢迎的 VTuber 来到公园播放和发布视频。这是<a href="https://twitter.com/yuika_siina" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>椎名</strong></a>由香、<a href="https://twitter.com/honmahimawari" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>本间</strong></a>向日葵和<a href="https://twitter.com/makaino_ririmu" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>魔井纪里梦</strong></a>第三次从虹山寺来访。时间尚未确定，但 VTuber 计划在 VRChat 中佩戴 mochipori 头像。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f823fb3276f9355eb3945b749bb550b4-kix.la54xy5rh2zu-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f823fb3276f9355eb3945b749bb550b4-kix.la54xy5rh2zu-1024x193.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f823fb3276f9355eb3945b749bb550b4-kix.la54xy5rh2zu-1024x193.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f823fb3276f9355eb3945b749bb550b4-kix.la54xy5rh2zu-300x57.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f823fb3276f9355eb3945b749bb550b4-kix.la54xy5rh2zu-768x145.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/f823fb3276f9355eb3945b749bb550b4-kix.la54xy5rh2zu-jpg.webp 1039w" width="1024" height="193" /></a></p><p>第一轮和第二轮分别是2月19日<a href="https://www.youtube.com/@omesis" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>欧米茄姐妹</strong></a>、2月23日<a href="https://twitter.com/Haneru_Inaba" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>稻叶羽流</strong></a>、3月1日<a href="https://twitter.com/n0ah_kurumi" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>狂三阿三</strong></a>和<a href="https://twitter.com/Ramune_Shirana3" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>白波弹珠</strong></a>。该发行版在每个 YouTube 频道上发布。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="如果 VTuber 举办结帐派对会发生什么？" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/5MoQfz_l65Q?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="【VRChat】今年再次进入VR世界！彻底调查虚拟彩虹乐园！ #Sanrio Vfes [Inaba Haneru / Nanashinku]" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com