bcbbff13a-kix.23a839rx9una-768x433.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.23a839rx9una-1536x866.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.23a839rx9una-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="577" /></a></p><p>目前由<a href="https://twitter.com/kamitsubaki_jp" target="_blank" rel="noopener">KAMITSUBAKI STUDIO</a>举办的培养下一代艺术家/创作者的选秀<a href="https://audition.kamitsubaki.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">“KAMITSUBAKI NEXT ARTISTS AUDITION 2024”</a>的申请期已延长至 3 月 17 日（星期日）23:59。</p><p>总制作人PIEDPIPER、艺术家以及神椿唱片和新海唱片的工作人员将参加本次试镜。</p><p>他们将从多方面的角度形成一个新的艺术项目。最优秀的候选人将获得适合其个性的活动计划，例如歌曲制作和为首次亮相做准备的课程。</p><p><a href="https://audition.kamitsubaki.jp/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">点击此处</a>查看特别试镜网站。</p><p> （参考） <a href="https://twitter.com/kamitsubaki_jp" target="_blank" rel="noopener">KAMITSUBAKI STUDIO X（原Twitter）</a></p><h2>虚拟偶像庆典“Life Like a Live!7”举行</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.k2jte8ep91xk-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.k2jte8ep91xk-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.k2jte8ep91xk-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.k2jte8ep91xk-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.k2jte8ep91xk-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.k2jte8ep91xk-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.k2jte8ep91xk-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p>虚拟偶像盛典“ <a href="https://lifelikealive.zan-live.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Life Like a Live!7</a> ”将于3月22日（星期五）至24日（星期日）在Z-aN举行。</p><p>来自<a href="https://twitter.com/dotLIVEyoutuber" target="_blank" rel="noopener">.LIVE</a> (Dot Live)、 <a href="https://twitter.com/774inc_official" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Nanashi Inku</a> 、 <a href="https://twitter.com/MarinasuChannel" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Marinasu</a> 、Tokui <a href="https://twitter.com/tokui_sorangley" target="_blank" rel="noopener">V Aozora</a> 、 <a href="https://twitter.com/rbc_geino" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Enogu</a> 、 <a href="https://twitter.com/gems_company" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GEMS COMPANY</a> 、 <a href="https://twitter.com/Re_AcT_" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Re:AcT</a>等的众多表演者将在 3 天的时间内总共 5 场演出。</p><p>除了每场演出的门票外，还提供观看全部 5 场演出的门票。点击<a href="https://www.zan-live.com/ja/live/detail/10403" target="_blank" rel="noopener">这里</a>购买门票。</p><p> (参考) <a href="https://twitter.com/LifeLikeaLive" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Life Like a Live!官方 (Elsuri) X (旧 Twitter)</a></p><h2> Racer VTuber Hanakan Kintone x “Cheer Drive”合作举行</h2><p><a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.m8259linwkrl-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.m8259linwkrl-1024x271.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.m8259linwkrl-1024x271.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.m8259linwkrl-300x79.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.m8259linwkrl-768x203.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.m8259linwkrl-jpg.webp 1200w" width="1024" height="271" /></a></p><p>赛车手 VTuber <a href="https://twitter.com/hanakakotone" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Kotone Hanakan</a>与共享经济服务“Cheer Drive”之间的合作项目“Racer VTuber Kotone Hanakan Collaboration: Drive around Town with KOTONE Racing”将于 3 月 20 日（星期三）至 6 月 23 日（星期三）举行（天）。</p><p> “Cheer Drive”是一项服务，驾驶员可以通过在汽车上贴上自己喜欢的品牌和内容的贴纸来支持公司和组织，作为回报，根据行驶距离获得福利。此次合作包括根据新绘制的插图制作成汽车贴纸的插图设计图案，以及KOTONE Racing标志设计图案。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://prtimes.jp/main/html/rd/p/000000104.000075261.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Cheer Drive Co., Ltd. 新闻稿</a></p><h2>九条林檎发行原创歌曲《Emotional night》</h2><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.age9vd2g1g9g-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.age9vd2g1g9g-1024x1024.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.age9vd2g1g9g-1024x1024.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.age9vd2g1g9g-300x300.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.age9vd2g1g9g-150x150.webp 150w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.age9vd2g1g9g-768x768.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/2edeb41ba696a883a0bd81abcbbff13a-kix.age9vd2g1g9g-jpg.webp 1350w" width="1024" height="1024" /></a></p><p>索尼音乐娱乐公司运营的虚拟人才开发和管理项目“ <a href="https://twitter.com/_vee_official_" target="_blank" rel="noopener">VEE</a> ”的<a href="https://twitter.com/ringo_0_0_5" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ringo Kujo</a>发布了原创歌曲“Emotional night”。</p><p> 《情感之夜》是由佐伯青年K作词、作曲、编曲的歌曲。此外，由晴明零执导的音乐录影带也已公开。</p><p><a href="https://kujoringo.lnk.to/Emotionalnight" target="_blank" rel="noopener">单击此处</a>查看音乐将在哪里分发。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="感人之夜 / 九条林檎 MV" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/RcZPN_Q8EeQ?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-me