-kix.hc9n0lh3rul-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.hc9n0lh3rul-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.hc9n0lh3rul-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.hc9n0lh3rul-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.hc9n0lh3rul-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.hc9n0lh3rul-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a></p><p><a href="https://twitter.com/773urara" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>浦良七海</strong></a>是一位往返于真实与虚拟之间的平行歌手。这将是我们第一次出现在 Sanrio Vfes。</p><p>从第一首歌开始，他们就拖着自己的原创歌曲《<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aJj5yJfXQ_E" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>红气球</strong></a>》出现在舞台后面，一边沿着花路一边唱一边向周围的观众挥手致意。阶段。她的头发和服装随着她的移动而移动。</p><p> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.vy84n48jzrgc-jpg.webp" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" src="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.vy84n48jzrgc-1024x576.webp" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" srcset="https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.vy84n48jzrgc-1024x576.webp 1024w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.vy84n48jzrgc-300x169.webp 300w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.vy84n48jzrgc-768x432.webp 768w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.vy84n48jzrgc-1536x864.webp 1536w, https://assets.moguravr.com/uploads/2024/03/05e3328c7dfb32b786d2025cb3b614ed-kix.vy84n48jzrgc-jpg.webp 1600w" width="1024" height="576" /></a><br /> <a href="https://assets.moguravr.c